                            </h2>
        
        
        
            </div>

    
        
        
    
        
    <p>CassavaGmarkets is a project that aims to improve the livelihoods of smallholder cassava farmers through better access to growth markets. It will explore climate change, pest and diseases, processing and gender. The countries this project will focus on are Ghana, Nigeria, Tanzania, Uganda and Malawi. India will also provide expertise.</p>

    
    
        
