    <p>Gratitude (Gains from Losses of Root and Tuber Crops) , led by the Natural Resources Institute (NRI), University of Greenwich UK, in collaboration with 15 other organisations, sought to help find solutions that will reduce waste from post-harvest losses of root and tuber crops and turn unavoidable waste into something of value.</p>

    
    
        
